cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SE 

The paper focuses on privacy concerns related to RFID tags and proposes a solution in the form of a mobile application. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber security (cs.CY). The application is designed to support customers in making privacy decisions, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the architecture of the application, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
